-- Avangardco Increases First-Quarter Egg Production by 11.3%
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-04-19T07:57:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-19/avangardco-increases-first-quarter-egg-production-by-11-3-.html
Avangardco Investments Public Ltd. (AVGR) ,
a Ukrainian egg producer, said output rose by 11.3 percent in
the first quarter compared with the year-earlier period, as the
number of hens increased.  Production climbed to 1.55 billion eggs from 1.39 billion,
Kiev-based Avangardco said today in an e-mailed statement.  Exports soared by 84.2 percent, to 110.8 million eggs, as
the company moved into new markets such as Mauritania and  Libya ,
according to the statement.  The average egg price increased by 37 percent from a year
earlier, Avangardco said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
